Reasoning: The paper discusses the development of a new algorithm for automatic segmentation of electron microscopy (EM) images using a convolutional neural network. This topic falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of supervised training and machine learning also suggests that the paper could be categorized under machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the use of EM images suggests that the paper could also be categorized under multimedia (cs.MM).
